INTERNSHIP_HUB
ğŸ“Œ Problem Statement

Finding genuine internship opportunities has always been a major challenge for students:

Students often struggle to identify authentic organizations that provide real internships.

Due to fake listings and lack of transparency, many students end up making wrong choices.

On the other hand, organizations also lack a simple and effective platform to showcase their internship opportunities.

To address this issue, INTERNSHIP_HUB was developed.

ğŸ’¡ Solution

INTERNSHIP_HUB is a web-based platform that bridges the gap between students and organizations:

Organizations can register themselves and post internship opportunities.

Students can sign up, log in, and browse available internships.

A secure authentication system ensures smooth access for both organizations and students.

The platform is designed to be simple, transparent, and user-friendly.

ğŸš€ Features

Organization registration & login

Student registration & login

Internship listings with details

Students can browse and explore internships

Secure authentication system

Clean and user-friendly interface

ğŸ› ï¸ Tech Stack

Backend: Django

Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript (Django Templates)

Database: SQLite (extendable to PostgreSQL/MySQL)

Version Control: Git & GitHub

ğŸ“‚ Project Structure
